Package com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.validator.pattern.attribute

Interface Summary
IDeployAttributeValidator Implemented by validators of a deploy model object attribute.
 

Class Summary
CapabilityAttributeToAttributePropagationValidator Utility class for validating the propagation of an attribute from the capability of a unit to the capability of another unit.
CapabilityAttributeUniqueInGroupValidator Validates that the attribute of a Capability is unique in the group of its Unit.
CapabilityAttributeUniqueInHostValidator Validates that the attribute of a Capability is unique in the host of its Unit.
CapabilityAttributeUniqueInLinkValidator Validates that the attribute of a Capability is unique in the between other units that are dependent on the same Capability through a Requirement.
CapabilityAttributeUniqueInTopologyValidator Validates that the attribute of a Capability is unique in the topology.
DeployAttributeNotEqualsValidator Validate that an attribute value does not belong to a set of invalid values.
DeployAttributeNotNullValidator Validates that an attribute of e deploy model object is not null.
DeployAttributeRestrictedValueValidator Validate that an attribute value belongs to a set of valid values.
DeployAttributeStringNotEmptyValidator Validates that an attribute of e deploy model object is not (not-null).
DeployAttributeValidator Base abstract implementation of the IDeployAttributeValidator interface.
DeployAttributeValueValidator Validates the value of an attribute delegating its computation to a subclass.
DeployRequirementAttributeNotNullValidator Validates that a Requirement contained RequirementExpression.getAttributeName().
DeployRequirementAttributeValidator Validates Requirement attributes of type Requirement.getDmoEType(), contained as RequirementExpression.getAttributeName().
